headline.print_headline: Nephew of 'Duck Dynasty' Patriarch to Run for Congress
headline.main: Nephew of 'Duck Dynasty' Patriarch to Run for Congress

lead_paragraph: The nephew of "Duck Dynasty" reality TV personality Phil Robertson said on Monday he would run for the U.S. House of Representatives in northeastern Louisiana as a conservative Republican.
